fr.inria.atlanmod.neoemf.data.store

Class NoopStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.inria.atlanmod.neoemf.data.mapping.AbstractDataMapper
      • fr.inria.atlanmod.neoemf.data.mapping.AbstractDataMapperChain<Backend>
        • fr.inria.atlanmod.neoemf.data.store.NoopStore
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ClassMapper, ContainerMapper, DataMapper, ManyReferenceMapper, ManyValueMapper, ReferenceMapper, ValueMapper, Saveable, Store, Closeable, AutoCloseable, Copiable<DataMapper>

    @ParametersAreNonnullByDefault
public class NoopStore
extends AbstractDataMapperChain<Backend>
implements Store
    A Store that simply notifies its associated Backend, without any additional operation.

    It corresponds to the tail of a Store chain and sets the default result for each method. These methods are handled if the Store that is supposed to handle them has not been configured during the store chain configuration.
